        <item>
            <title>【評測】《SEED FREEDOM》MR 魂飛昇自由高達　更好的外觀 + 合金關節</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/17/mrfreedom/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mrfreedom</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/17/mrfreedom/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 04:30:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220411</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日，《機動戰士高達 SEED FREEDOM》劇場版成為動漫熱門話題，雖然香港尚未上映，但網上已有大部份的劇透了……而日本票房逾 26.8 億日元，成迄今為止票房最高的劇場版高達，超越 1982 年上映的《機動戦士ガンダムIII めぐりあい宇宙篇》，實在很想看啊&#8230;&#8230;</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220414" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gglwrzwasaazhe-1-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gglwrzwasaazhe-1-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gglwrzwasaazhe-1.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>在這波高達熱潮中，Metal Robot 魂系列的飛昇自由高達（Rising Freedom Gundam）引起了不少關注。相較於同期發售的 HG 和 SD 版本，Metal Robot 魂的飛昇自由高達以更優秀的造型和細節處理吸引眾多粉絲。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220415" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6651.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MR 魂飛昇自由高達的開箱內容豐富，包含了主體模型、底座以及眾多精緻的小配件。其獨特的配色方案，與傳統的自由高達有所不同，不過這是動畫的設定了，特別是那種藍色……</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6653-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6653-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6653.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6654-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6654-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6654.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">後備天線</p><p>不過 MR 魂飛昇自由高達在細節處理上表現出色，如身上的 Marking，合金關節和部分金屬腳掌的使用，增加了整體的質感和重量感，使模型即便背負重量較大的揹包翅膀，也能夠穩固地站立。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6658-553x580.jpg" alt="" width="553" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6658-553x580.jpg 553w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6658.jpg 858w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 553px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220419" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6660-528x580.jpg" alt="" width="528" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6660-528x580.jpg 528w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6660.jpg 819w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 528px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220420" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6662-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6662-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6662.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220421" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6663-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6663-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6663.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220422" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6664-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6664-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6664.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6665-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6665-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6665.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在可動性方面，MR 魂飛昇自由高達有不錯的表現，頭部、腰部以及四肢的活動範圍充分，使得模型能夠擺出多種動態姿勢。此外，模型配備了豐富的武器和配件，包括步槍、鐳射軍刀特效、多功能盾牌等，不僅可以重現片中的經典武裝展開和收納狀態，還能展示招牌的全砲火展開模式，增添了不少玩賞價值。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6666-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6666-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6666.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6667-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6667-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6667.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6668-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6668-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6668.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6669-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6669-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6669.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6670-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6670-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6670.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6673-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6673-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6673.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6674-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6674-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/dsc6674.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>不過都有點小問題，如裙甲很易脫落，MA 形態的變形設計忠於原著那樣，這個都是算了吧，不太想擺那個 MA 形態出來了。<script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6681" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53533174015/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53533174015_a943686c2d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6681" width="1024" height="944" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6695" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53533066319/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53533066319_fdf2ed210a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6695" width="1024" height="906" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6689" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53533174010/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53533174010_d59a3646d7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6689" width="1024" height="742" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6706" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53532930793/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53532930793_ccd7a8ef06_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6706" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6709" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53532930788/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53532930788_301fd299bd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6709" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC6716" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53531855802/in/album-72177720314822220/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53531855802_194c0b4f6b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6716" width="1024" height="757" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">MA 形態如果係咁樣會唔會好睇啲？<script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>綜合來看，Metal Robot 魂系列的飛昇自由高達在品質和細節上都有不錯的表現，是值得收藏的。期待《機動戰士高達 SEED FREEDOM》系列能帶來更多精彩的模型及玩具，滿足廣大 Fans。</p><p>查詢：瑞華行</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/17/mrfreedom/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】《SEED FREEDOM》MR 魂飛昇自由高達　更好的外觀 + 合金關節</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
